\id 1TI - Northern Paiute NT -USA 2012 (DBL -2013)
\h 1 Timothy
\toc1 Paul ka Timothy-matoo Mooe Tubona
\toc2 1 Timothy
\toc3 1 Tm
\mt1 Paul ka Timothy-matoo Mooe Tubona
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Nuga tubona, Paul, e pua'a, Timothy-matoo. Nu mooasoo Te Pabe'e-witu u tunedyoo'epu mu Te Naa God Te Pabe'e Jesus-no meeoo e netamma, “Mu numu tuukwe ka Mu Pabe'e-witu.” Soo Te Naa togesapa te magwetzoipu. Te Pabe'e tamme poonnekwu ka pumatoo te nanetzakwiyina. O'no tamme oo-wa'ne'yookwu.
\v 2 Nu u sopedakwatoo. U togesoo oo naka'oedyukute ka ume e tuukwena ka Te Pabe'e Jesus-witu. Nu meeoo u nanesootuhikute soo Te Naa ka Te Pabe'e Jesus-no sakwa besa u mabetsea, u sootuhina, u magwetzoi.
\p 
\v 3 Nu ka gi soo Macedonia-witoo meana, “U sakwa yaa Ephesus-wizoo,” mee nu u tubetse netamma. “U sakwa mu numu nemooagadu tunedyooe mu tuukwe umu sakwa nukatu tunedyooe-kwa'nekoosoo mu tunedyooe.”
\v 4 Umu sakwa gi mu Jew numu pumme tunedyooena tumayohokupana, yise kukumma'akoosoo numu pumme tunedyooena gi nakabetseapana. Oosoo ooonne'yoo numu pukwi nanahana, ka oo tu namane-kwi umu Te Naa gi naka'oedyukute. Pana soo Te Naa meeoo te tubetse netamma, “Nuka suu'mu naka'oedyuku.”
\p 
\v 5 Sumuba na'unnedu soo Te Naa meeoo te netamma, “Nanasoobedyana ka nu-kwitu tubetse tunaka'oedyuku kaaheno nuga podo meano.”
\v 6 Susumudu numu ka Te Naa besa po ooemota maneyugwe. Umuoo sukwe apegea, gi hekwitu nehanepana.
\v 7 Umuoo ka mu Jew numu tumayohona gi nakasopedakwatoopana numu too'e tunedyooe.
\v 8 Ka moomooasoo soo Moses nanamoo'atupu mu Jew numu tumayohona te tuukwe'e oosoo besa'yoo ka pumme tu nakasopedakwatoo.
\v 9 Tamme sakwa oo nakasopedakwadoo ka mu Jew numu tumayohona ka mu tunaka'oedyukudu too suta'yoo, umu too'e natunedyooena gi ka mooasoo besa'yoo numu-doo. Mu ooonne'yoo suta'yoo numu: Ka Te Naa-witu suda nanatuukwedu, tu naanapua'amu mesoo goena, kumma'akoosoo numu mesoo goena.
\v 10 Kukummanosoo nana'aheegoena, numu tooe tuduhana, esagoena, suda nana-witu na'esagoena, tooe how tooe manakwe.
\v 11 Yow esoo Te Naa unnepu oo tuukwena. Soo Te Naa meeoo e netamma, “No'oko mu numu nuga besa unnepu tuukwe.”
\p 
\v 12 Nu ka Te Pabe'e nesookwuga'e unu oo nakabetsea. Nuka oosoo sakwa e nakabetsea e sooyugwena soo Te Pabe'e nuka netutzeapu.
\v 13 O'nosoo nu gisoo tunaka'oedyukuna ka Jesus suda netammana, ka oo nanumu kusegeana, nu tookwa ka Te Pabe'e wohonepana, gi oo nakasopedakwatoo. Ooonne'yoopana soo Te Pabe'e e sootuhipu.
\v 14 Soo Te Pabe'e tunaka'oedyuku e mayugwe.
\v 15 Soo tooe haga tooe tubetse togesapa yadoo'a ka meeoo unnena, “Soo Te Pabe'e ka te teepu-kooba petu mu sutakoo numu putamme manese mu magwetzoikwuse.” Nu yow uga tubetse suta'yoo numu.
\v 16 Pana soo Te Pabe'e Jesus e sootuhipu. Ooonne'yoona mu tzapoonnekute, te mesoo sootuha'e tuwazoo too'e ka pumme te woho'ne sapa. Meno'o yise tuwazoo te tzapoonnekute umu pumme naka'oedyukudu magwetzoina.
\v 17 Numme oo nesookwuga'e, “U, Ne Naa ooosapa ne moohenummekwudu, gi mobekwa-ga'yoo. U Ne Tubetse Naa. Gi haga u poonnedu. Tooe haga tooe, tooe hanotu tooe, sakwa ooosapa u nesootuhimo.”
\p 
\v 18 E pua'a, Timothy, nu meeoo u netamma u sakwa oo tubetse nakabetsea ka Te Pabe'e Jesus no'oko hekwitu ka meeoo ume oo pooha netamma-kwa'nesoo. U oo soomayu ka o'nosoo mu numu u-makoo poohabe poonne.
\v 19 U sakwa ooosapa Te Naa unnepu naka'oedyukuna o'no u ooosapa besa manenokwu. Susumudu numu oe tu tunaka'oedyuku soomu'wa umu ka gi tubetse besa tu soonamme-kwikoo hemma mayohona.
\v 20 Soo Hymenaeus-no Alexander mee naneadu ooonne'yoo. Nu ka suda-tamme umu tzamuna umu sakwa oo natunedyooese, gi ka Te Naa suda netammadooa. O'no saa'a suda tu unnepu nematzagase soo Te Naa o'no mu sootuhidooa.
\c 2
\p 
\v 1 Tamme sakwa no'oko tooe hownnekoo tooe numu nanesootuhiku soo Te Naa sakwa mu sootuhi, tamme yise Te Naa oowetoo netubetse'a.
\v 2 No'obatusoo mu numu moohedu tamme sakwa nanesootuhiku tuwazoo. O'no yise umu gi te wohonena tamme ka besa podo gi namatzamana mesoo meadabekwu.
\v 3 Tamme ka mu numu moohedu nanesootuhikuna, o'no yise Te Naa ookow besa'yookute.
\v 4 Mu numu sakwa no'yoona ka Te Naa-witu besa nakasopedakwatoo, Te Naa no'oko numu soomagwetzoa'e.
\v 5-6 Soo Te Naa suu'mu pumatoo te nanesootuhina. Soo Te Pabe'e Jesus tubetse numu mane. Tamme-kooba nabatsase te magwetzoi. Soo Te Pabe'e te naamookwi manepunne. O'no soo Te Pabe'e suu'mu ka tamme Te Naa noko nanapua'amu mayugwedooa. Soo Te Naa meeoo mu numu tuukwe.
\v 7 Soo Te Naa nuka yise netutzeapu mu gi Jew numu tunesootabue mee unnena.
\v 8 Mu naana tooe hanotu tooe sakwa Te Naa-matoo nanesootuhi. Umu sakwa gi sutapana, gi nanahapana ka nanesootuhina. Ka suda tu manena nematzagase o'no besa ka Te Naa-matoo nanesootuhina.
\p 
\v 9 Mu momoko'ne sakwa punno'o besa tunaka'oedyukuna besa nanesootuhi-no. Umu sakwa gi tu nagwe a tubua-ma mu numu nasootza'mekupana, gi how tuwazoo tu tzopuhu-ma namadabue-ma nasootza'mepana gi ka besa tatabuadu-ma namasooapana tuwazoo.
\v 10 Mu momoko'ne sakwa besa mu tumatugukugena, o'no mu numu mu posopedakwadoona, umu tookwa tubetse tunaka'oedyukudu mee mu sooyugwe.
\v 11 No'yoona mu momoko'ne sakwa oo nakapunne ka pummetu tunedyoo'e. Gi pummesoo tusooyugwena wahapana.
\v 12 Gi sakwa mu momoko'ne ka mu naana puu tunemadabueku, tuwazoo gi mu naana tunedyooe. Umuoo momoko'ne sakwa gi unnepana.
\v 13 Soo nana, Adam mee naneadu mooe namanumudoopu, o'no yise soo mogo'ne Eve mee naneadu oobenakwatu namadabue.
\v 14 Soo Adam gi nanemooagapu pana soo Eve yise nanemooagase suda mooe tumatugupu.
\v 15 Ka 'yoo manena mu momoko'ne namagwetzoi umu yise ka oe tunaka'oedyukuna ka tooa'adoona gi no'osoo nummabodona besa oo-toogoo tsebooenokwu yise ka Te Naa besa podo meadabenokwu.
\c 3
\p 
\v 1 Esoo na'unnedu togesapa, “Gi nasookwipana ka nananesootuhidu moohena esoo besa'yoo.”
\p 
\v 2-3 Ka mu nananesootuhidu moohedu sakwa kaaheno besa tumatugudu. Umu sakwa no'yoona nanasu'mu nonodukwa-ga. Umu sakwa gi suda-ma nama'emukwa, besa tutusooyugwedu, gi numu nasootza'mekupana tuwazoo. Umu sakwa ka mu numu tummatzi ka tooe hekwi tooe. Umu sakwa gi puusoo ewow hemma sookwipana, umu gi baagoedu. Umu sakwa gi nidyupupana, gi etzaga sutapana, besa ooosapa numu matugu.
\v 4-5 Umu sakwa besa numu tunedyooedu. Umu sakwa oo sopedakwatoo ka tu nodukwa no'oko tu dooamu tunemadabueku, o'no umu tu naa nakabetseakwu. Umu ka gi pummesoo dooamu meeoo tunedyooena, umu tookwa gi ka Te Naa dooamu meeoo tunedyooe-wa'ne'yoo.
\v 6 Umu sakwa gi pudu tunaka'oedyukudu. Umu ka ooonne'yoona sumuna paba nasooyugwekwu. Soo suda tu tumatuguna umu-matoosoo kodyukwu ka Sutakoo tu yugwe-kwa'nesoo.
\v 7 Umu sakwa mu gi tunaka'oedyukudu-tamme kaaheno'yoo besa mu nematugu, o'no yise numu gi mu nesootzema-wa'ne'yoo. Ka mu numu sumuna umu nesootze'ma soo suta'yoo suda-kwi mu mesoo mayugwe.
\p 
\v 8-10 Mu numu nanesootuhidu tummatzikwudu sakwa besa na'eya'ese o'no sakwa umu nanetutzea. Mu tunaka'oedyukudu sakwa oo mooe sopedakwatoo ka besa'yoona. Umu nanetutzeadu sakwa ka Te Naa podo besa tu meakwuna tzapoonne umu sakwa gi esagoepana, gi baagoepana, gi numu tu'ooepana, gi puusoo hemma natoogoo soogwipana tuwazoo. Ka Te Pabe'e Jesus-wi tunaka'oedyukuna ka puusoo nasopedakwadoona ka Te Naa besa podo meana.
\p 
\v 11 Mu pepeawabe ka mu nanesootuhidu tummatziwabe sakwa punno'o besa'yoo. Umu sakwa gi numu nesootzemapana, gi etzaga ha'yoo tooe naneyugwepana, ooosapa kaaheno besa tumatuguna o'no besa'yoo.
\v 12 Mu nanesootuhidu tutummatziwabe sakwa nanasusumu nonodukwa-ga, mu doodooamu sakwa punno'o besa mu nakabetsea, no'oko tu nobe-witu meeoo tunedyooe tuwazoo.
\v 13 Umu ka besa mu nanesootuhidu tutummatzina mu numu besa mu sooyugwe. Umuoo gi nasookwina Te Pabe'e Jesus-witu wahakwu.
\p 
\v 14-15 Nu yabesoo u-baa soopetuga'a pana sumuna nu gi oo mane-wa'ne'yoo. Ooonne'yoona nu u-matoo tubo'o, o'no yise u ka Te Tubetse Naa-matoo nanesootuhibu kaaheno mu numu tunedyooe.
\p 
\v 16 Ka Te Pabe'e-ma numme tunekwu'u.
\q1 Te Pabe'e yaa teepu-kooba tamme-wa'nesoo nadooa'adoopu. Soo Te Naa Besa Pooha oo tzapoonne oosoo Te Naa Besa Tooa'a. Oobe pa'atoo tamme-koobatoosoo ka Te Naa-baatoo oosoo kodyuka. No'obatusoo numu ka Te Pabe'e-witu nawahana nakakoo. Yise tooe hano tooe susumudu numu oe tunaka'oedyukute.
\c 4
\p 
\v 1 Soo Te Naa Besa Pooha te tuukwe'e ka saa'a susumudu tunaka'oedyukudu ka Te Pabe'e besa podo tu meana ma'wukakwu, ka tooe hownnekoo tooe sutakoo poohabe naka'oedyukuna pumme nemooagadu.
\v 2 Mu numu sutakoo tunedyooena umuoo numu nemooaga. Umu numu nemooagadu ka wuna'me suda tumatuguna, umu yise ka kaaheno besow gi oo sopedakwatoo.
\v 3-4 “Gi nananodukwadoopana, gi no'o-baatoosoo tukapu tukapana,” mee mu numu nemooagadu numu netamma, pana soo Te Naa ka no'oko tukapu tamme-too matabuepu. Soo Te Naa no'okosoo hemma besa matabuepu yise gi hee suta'yoo ka oo-koobatoo te nanesootuha'e.
\v 5 Soo Te Naa unnepu ka tukapu-koobatoo te nanesootuhino'o, tamme gi oo namanabuekute.
\p 
\v 6 U ka Te Pabe'e besa tummatza'e ka umu tunaka'oedyukudu tuukwena ka ume e tuukwe-kwitu. U uusoo besa natunedyooe ka besa na'unnedu nagenona.
\v 7 Ka umu na'esayaedu numu tunedyooedu u sakwa gi nakabetseapana. U sakwa ka Te Naa besa po tubetse nageno. Oo-makoo natunedyooena.
\v 8 Esoo u tookoo u mabetseana besa'yoo, pana soo Te Naa besa podo numu meanona unusoo besa'yoo. Oosoo Te Naa podo nameadu numu natunedyooena besa'yoo, ka oo-toogoo meanona unusoo besa'yoo. Oosoo Te Naa podo nameadu numu natunedyooena besa'yoo ka meno'o yaa'a ka teepu-kooba'yoona pana ka saa'a Te Naa-matoo te mease oosoo unusoo besa'yoo.
\v 9 Soo meeoo ume e tuukwena togesapa. U sakwa a nageno.
\v 10 Nu ka tubetse besow po nageno'o, soo Te Naa no'oko numu besa matugu, ka pukwi u tunaka'oedyuku u magwetzoikwu.
\p 
\v 11 No'oko numu tunedyooe umu sakwa ka ume e tuukwena nageno.
\v 12 U sakwa no'oko numu soopedya, o'no mu numu ume sootubetseya'ekwu, yise tubetse unudooe besa'yoo. U sakwa ka Te Naa besa podo meanona mu tunaka'oedyukudu u poonnena punno'o u-kwa'nesoo. O'no gi haga sakwa meeoo u netamma, “U nagutza naatse numme u tunedyooe-kwi.”
\p 
\v 13 Ooosapa ka mu numu Te Naa unnepu-witu tunedyooeno, e petuno'otoo tooe.
\v 14 Mu wakwa'etse u pooha poonnena, u nanesootuhikute. Umuoo u-ma matuguse soo Te Naa ka nanesootuhibu noko numu u tunedyooekwuna ooka u sootuhi. U sakwa ooosapa Te Naa unnepu-witu numu tunedyooe. Gi u namatusookwunikwu.
\v 15 U sakwa e tunetamma tubetse nagenona, o'no yise mu numu u poonnena u sopedakwadookwu ka unusoo besa u maneno'o.
\v 16 Besakoo tunakabetseana, besakoo ka Te Naa unnepu suu'mu numu tunedyooena, u ka ume nakabetseadu-no namagwetzoikwu.
\c 5
\p 
\v 1 Tooe mu wakwa'etse tuma'emukwa sapa gi mu nasakwa'ekupana, besakoo ooka mu nemadabuekuna, u naa u nemadatugu-kwa'nesoo. Mu naana sakwa u pabe'e-wa'nesoo nematugu.
\v 2 Mu pepeawabe u pea-wa'ne, mu momoko'ne u punne'e-wa'ne. Gi suda umu-tamme tusooyugwepana.
\p 
\v 3-4 Umu pepeawabe gi kookoomamu-gakoo, umuoo mu doodooamu-no mu mooamu sakwa mu mabetsea. O'nosoo umu naanapua'amu mu mananase umu ka tu naanapua'amu mooatupugoese, o'no yise mu doodooamu sakwa mu mabetsea. Oo umu manena Te Naa tunetammana mayohona ka Te Naa besa masoonammekute. Mu doodooamu sakwa Te Naa nakabetsea. Umu gi kookoomamu-ga'yoo, gi nanumu-ga'yoo.
\p 
\v 5 Mu gi kookoomamu-ga'yoo gi nananumu-ga'yoo, “Soo Te Naa ne mabetseakwu,” mee sokwama. Ooosapa Te Naa-tamme nanesootuhino'o. Umu ooonne'yoo sakwa mu tunaka'oedyukudu mabetsea.
\v 6 Susumudu gi kookoomamu-ga'yoo gi kaaheno Te Naa podo meadu ooosapa puusoo tu nasoo'yugwetoo manedu, gi Te Naa-nakwana nakwitu soonammedu, umuoo gi hee.
\v 7 “Umu gi kookoomamu-ga'yoo sakwa ka besow tumayohope nagena o'no umu gi haga mu nesootzema-wa'ne'yoo,” mee sakwa u mu tuukwe.
\v 8 Mu tunaka'oedyukudu mee naneyugwedu ka gi pummesoo tu nobe-witu manepunnena mabetseana ka tu nanumu-too gi mabetsea umu oo tzapoonne ka gi Te Pabe'e-wi tu tunaka'oedyukuna. Umu yise mu numu gi soo tunaka'oedyukudu ooonakwa suta'yoo.
\p 
\v 9 Mu gi kookoomamu-ga'yoo ka nanesootuhi tummatzidu mane-kwitu, ooonnekoo u sakwa netutzea. Mooasoo pepeawabena, sumusoo koomadoopu,
\v 10 mu numu sakwa oo sopedakwatoo ka besa mu tumatuguna, tu doodooamu besa mabetseapu, wakwawa'a besa matuguna, mu tunaka'oedyukudu tummatzina, mu tutuha manedu numu tuwow, yise no'obatusoo besa matugudu.
\p 
\v 11-13 Mu sususu'a tu kookoomamu tuikupu sakwa gi mu numu nanesootuhibu-wi tutummatzipana, ka gisoo pepeawabena. Umu toetzegoekwu oona nonobe-too meana numu nesootzemana gi pumme nehane-kwitu sapa ewa tuukwena. Tooe umu ka Te Pabe'e, “Ooosapa nu mu nanesootuhi tummatzikwu,” mee netammase sapa, umu sumuna koomadoose ka tu unnepu gi mayohokwu.
\p 
\v 14 Nu meeoo mu netamma mu gi kookoomamu-ga'yoo sususu'a sakwa koomadoose ka dooamu-gana mu mabetsea, ka mu tu nobe-witu tuwazoo. O'no umu gi nanesootze'ma.
\v 15 Umu-matu mooasoo ka Te Naa besa po ma'wukase, ka sutakoo podo manekapu.
\v 16 Mu gi kookoomamu-ga'yoo ka mu tunaka'oedyukudu-nagatu nanumu-gana, umuoosoo sakwa mu mabetsea. O'no yise mu tunaka'oedyukudu, gi kookoomamu-gakoo, gi oekoo nanumu-gakoo, gi natummatzidu, umuoo sakwa umu tummatzi.
\p 
\v 17 Mu wakwa'etse ka besa tunematuguna umuoo sakwa ka mu numu nanesootuhipe tunedyooe yise oo-koobakwisoo natumanakakwu.
\v 18 Soo Te Naa unnena ooonne'yoona mee nabotugupu, “Soo pookoo puu ka numu yasa tummatzise umu sakwa oo-matoo mesoo tuka.” Yise, “Soo tooe haga tooe numu tummatzidu sakwa punno'o natumanakaku ka tu tutummatzi-kwi.”
\p 
\v 19 Tamme gi numu naka'oedyukupana ka mu numu moohedu mu wakwa'etse nesootzema. Waahoo tooetoo pihoo numu ooka suda oo tumatuguna poonnedusoo ookow waha, mu saa'a mu naka'oedyukudooa.
\v 20 U sakwa ka mu wakwa'etse-matu suda tumatugudu numu-koobenatoo bi, o'no umu susumudu saa'a gi oo-wa'nesoo manedooa.
\v 21 No'oko nanana sumu-kwa'nesoo nematugu. Nu ka mu Te Naa, Te Pabe'e Jesus ka umu Te Naa tutummatzidu-no ka nuka tu tunemanekuna u tuukwe, “U sakwa no'oko Te Naa unnepu nakabetseana gi numu tutzeapana.”
\v 22 U ka numu moohedu manekwuse, oetu mooe soohanenummese, o'no u ka u mi-ma oo-ma matuguse oo nanesootuhikukwu. Ka numu suda manakwe gi umu-ma tzabepana. Ooosapa besa tumatuguno.
\v 23 Ka baa hebena gi ookow suu'mu hebepana, huutsekoo atsa tutza'emukwa baa tuwazoo, o'no u numua-witu besa yugwekwu. O'no yise u gi ooosapa tuoeya'e.
\v 24 Susumudu numu ka suda tumatuguse no'yoona numu oo sopedakwatoo ka meno'o. Susumudu numu ka suda tu tumatuguna tooe watsetugupana mu numu saa'a oetu naka.
\v 25 Susumudu ka besa manena no'yoona numu oo sopedakwadoo. Tooe mu numu gi oo nakase sapa, saa'a umu oo sopedakwadoo, gi oosoo ooosapa nawatsetugu.
\c 6
\p 
\v 1 No'yoona mu numu ka hemma how yugwena sakwa ka meeoo pumme nedyawedu nakabetsea tooe nawanga'a-wa'ne manepunnepana.
\v 2 Mu numu hemma how yugwedu sakwa tubetse tunakabetse'a umu ka mu tunaka'oedyukudu tummatzina ka besa mu soobedyana.
\p 
\v 3 Umu atasoo numu tunedyooedu gi ka Te Pabe'e Jesus besa unnepu nagedu,
\v 4 umu meeoo nasooyugwedu, “Numme numu ooonakwa unu sokwama,” mee'e, pana umu gi hemma sopedakwatoo. Umu numu-no tu nanepeduguna nananuusoogwedukuna, nanasagwa'ekuna suda nananetammana, suda manakwe.
\v 5 Soo numu ka sukwe nanahana gi ka toge-kwitu sopedakwatoo. Umu numu meeoo sokwama soo tooe haga tooe ka Te Naa besa podo meana ewow hemma hee-gakoo. Pana gi!
\v 6 Mu numu ka Te Naa besa podo meana gi hemma soogwa'e, mooasoo besa nasootuha'e.
\p 
\v 7 Tamme ka nadooa'adoose, gi hee-gana yaa'a teepu-kooba numu petu tamme yise ka ya'ese no'okosoo hemma yaanoko te heetoo'apu ma'wukakwu.
\v 8 Tamme ka tukapu noko ka pukwi te namasuana mooasoo hee-gana gi hemmasoo soosookwi-wa'ne tabua.
\v 9 Mu numu ka ewahoosoo hemma soogwina besakoo nanemooagakwu. Umu tubetse unu hemma soogwikwu oosoosoo yise kadoo mu mayugwekwu.
\v 10 No'obatusoo soo suta'yoo tamme-tamme kemmakwu ka unusoo te tusoogwipunne. Susumudu numu ka unu tusoogwina umuoo ka Te Naa besa po ooemota manekayakwe, yise puusoo suda namasokwamayakwe.
\p 
\v 11 Timothy, u mow Te Naa tubetse naka'oedyukudu. Gi hemma sookwipana ka Te Naa besa po nageno'o: Besa tumatuguna, tubetse tunaka'oedyukuna, no'oko numu soobedyana, besa numu matuguna. Ooosapa oo nageno tooe hemma tooe how manegena sapa.
\v 12 U sakwa tubetse unusoo ka Te Naa-wi tunaka'oedyuku. Uusoo nanemabetseano, o'no saa'a Te Naa-matoo besakoo meadooa. U dea'a ka Te Naa tunetammana mayohona u baa-wi namatzakana ewow numu tunedyoo'e ka umu natunedyooepu-witu.
\v 13-14 Soo Te Naa no'oko hemma nemamakwupu ookahoo soo Te Pabe'e-no umuoo\f + \fr 6:13-14 \ft Ka Pontius Pilate besa nanekwahakute tuukwe'e.\f* nuka tunemanekuna nu u tuukwe, “Ka eka besa na'unnedu Te Pabe'e Jesus yaa teepu-koobasoo oo kodyu petukwuno'otoo sakwa u tunaka'oedyukuna.”
\v 15 Ka Te Naa tu sooyugwena oe manepetuse, soo Te Pabe'e kodyu petudooa soo Te Naa o unu pooha-ga'yoo, no'oko hemma nemadabuedu, no'oko hemma ooonakwa nadu'yadu. Tamme ooosapa oo nesookwugikwu.
\v 16 Te Naa suu'mu numu magwetzoidu, gi mobekwa-ga'yoo. Oosoo no'oko hemma ooonakwakoo pooha-gana soo oo pooha oo na'oonnakwi kootabedooapunnedu-kwa'ne tabuapunne. Gi hemma putsage'e mane-wa'ne'yoo, ka unu oo pooha-gakoo. Gi haga oo poonnedu. Gi haga oo poonne-wa'ne'yoo. Tuwow no'yoona numu tooe hanotu tooe sakwa oo-matoo nanesootuhi. Numu ooosapa sakwa oo tubetseyi, no'yoona hemma oosoo nematunagakwudu. Togesapa.
\p 
\v 17 Ka mu numu ewow hee-gakoo meeoo netamma, “Gi ka mu numu ooonakwa besa nasooyugwepana.” Umu sakwa gi ka hemma tu hee-ga-ma nasoonatzipana, ka Te Naa-ma suu'mu nasoonatzi. Oosoo no'oko hemma-ma te sootuhina besa pumatoo te masokwamana, oosoo ka no'okosoo hemma hee-gana.
\v 18-19 Umu ewow hee-ga'yoo sakwa besa tumatuguna ka numu besa tummatzi. Umu sakwa mu tutuha manedu mesoo hee-maka. Soo Te Naa ka oo mu tumatuguse ka hemma besa mu hee-ga-ma umu-matoo makodyukwuse, o'no saa'a umu nasootuhikwu ka Te Naa-baa petugase.
\v 20 E pua'a Timothy, ooosapa oo sumayu ka Te Naa ume netammapu. Gi ka mu numu ooosapa nanahadu no'oko hemma nesopedakwatoo mee unnedu nakabetseapana.
\v 21 Susumudu gi kaaheno tunakabetseana umu yise ka Te Pabe'e po ooemota manekayakwe. “Soo Te Naa sakwa u tubetse sootuhi,” mee'e nu u nanesootuhikute.
